{"tid":2277342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WHO 譚德塞發文祝賀拜登：期待與您合作","createTime":"2020-11-08T11:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T16:04:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"a87420ab6c0bc9a36756c18ac2bf1e4a36be12e4","tid":2277342,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨總統候選人拜登(Joe Biden)當選總統，預料將取消現任總統川普7月啟動退出世界衛生組織(WHO)的程序。世衛秘書長譚德塞(Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus)今天(8日)祝賀拜登並表示「期待與您的團隊合作」。<br />\n<br />\n美國2020激烈選戰過後，拜登在美國時間7日晚間發表勝選演說，呼籲全國團結並將以抗疫為第一要務。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞今天在推特發文祝賀拜登及副手賀錦麗(Kamala Harris)當選，表示自己與世衛同仁「期待與您及您的團隊合作」。<br />\n<br />\n他也說，2019年冠狀病毒疾病(COVID-19)大流行危機顯示，全球團結對於保護生命至關重要。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2020/05/19/ce3e71853d6e3d1967a99cbad54ff4b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2020%2F05%2F19%2Fce3e71853d6e3d1967a99cbad54ff4b8.jpg&h=5dd89d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2084203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2084203&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7xZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=d96c1949\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2084203</a>"},{"pid":"7bd693c3eae8b2e8aba853ed0af75f8b8f99a5db","tid":2277342,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896cc7de4ed82bc13aaddc19dbc6272ebaa3b5e1","tid":2277342,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\"><span class=\"medium\"><strong>[⇩ 民主左派 = 支共⇩]<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">[⇩ 左膠 = 西方粉紅